    "description": "Hexaware Technologies Global Group is actively seeking a talented and motivated Senior Software Engineer to join our dynamic team in Chandigarh. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Hexaware Technologies Global Group:\nHexaware Technologies Global Group is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in Docker\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chandigarh, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Hexaware Technologies Global Group!",
